ZH: 我昨天做了一个奇怪的梦。
EN: Yesterday, I had a strange dream.
ZH: 昨晚我做了一个关于飞行的梦。
EN: Last night, I had a dream about flying.
ZH: 她经常做梦，但很少记得梦境内容。
EN: She often dreams but rarely remembers the content of her dreams.
ZH: 我有时梦到我已经毕业了，但实际上还有一年的学业要完成。
EN: Sometimes I dream that I have already graduated, but in reality there is another year of study to complete.
ZH: 她曾经做梦成为一名世界著名的歌手。
EN: She once dreamt of becoming a world-famous singer.
ZH: 我的梦想是环游世界。
EN: My dream is to travel around the world.
ZH: 他小时候的梦想是成为一名医生。
EN: His childhood dream was to become a doctor.
ZH: 我们应该追随自己的梦想，努力实现。
EN: We should follow our dreams and work hard to achieve them.
ZH: 家是我最美好的梦境。
EN: Home is my happiest dream.
ZH: 每个人都有追寻梦想的权利。
EN: Everyone has the right to pursue their dreams.
ZH: 梦想需要勇气和努力来实现。
EN: Dreams require courage and effort to achieve.
ZH: 她的梦想是成为一名优秀的科学家。
EN: Her dream is to become an excellent scientist.
ZH: 梦境是我们内心深处的表达。
EN: Dreams are expressions of our innermost thoughts.
ZH: 在我的梦中，我在一个美丽的花园里漫步。
EN: In my dream, I stroll through a beautiful garden.
ZH: 梦想的实现需要时间和耐心。
EN: Achieving dreams takes time and patience.
ZH: 我的梦境中总是出现一只小猫。
EN: A little cat always appears in my dreams.
ZH: 睡梦是大脑休息和充电的方式。
EN: Dreaming is a way for the brain to rest and recharge.
ZH: 她告诉我她昨晚做了一个预示未来的梦。
EN: She told me she had a dream last night that foreshadowed the future.
ZH: 他的梦中总是出现一只飞翔的鹰。
EN: An eagle flying always appears in his dreams.
ZH: 梦想是人类的一种力量。
EN: Dreams are a kind of human power.
